# 3️⃣ Important concept (Interview point)

Hibernate `save()` behave like:

| Condition                 | Operation |
| ------------------------- | --------- |
| id null                   | INSERT    |
| id exists in DB           | UPDATE    |
| id exists but row missing | Exception |

Nee case lo **3rd case jarigindi**.

